    <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/DToC/NavigateToC.dita" xtrc="title:1;4:12">Navigating text in the table of contents</title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Users/megan/Desktop/DocumentationAll/DITA_Files-Various_Applications/DToC/NavigateToC.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:16">The Table of Contents displays terms selected (from the left column) and lets users
